20
00:01:32,320 --> 00:01:34,400

21
00:01:39,740 --> 00:01:42,320

22
00:01:42,320 --> 00:01:48,140

23
00:01:49,271 --> 00:01:52,030

24
00:01:52,840 --> 00:01:55,820

25
00:01:55,820 --> 00:01:58,550

26
00:02:02,580 --> 00:02:04,240
Let's do it here.

27
00:02:04,240 --> 00:02:06,500
Are you sure?

28
00:02:06,500 --> 00:02:10,660
You are under my phase. I can kill you within six palms attack.

29
00:02:10,660 --> 00:02:12,660
Is that so?

30
00:02:13,620 --> 00:02:17,900
If so, I will kill you with a higher phase.

31
00:02:19,980 --> 00:02:22,520
How cocky.

32
00:02:25,540 --> 00:02:27,760
Lend me your sword.

33
00:02:39,980 --> 00:02:44,340
I was touched by an immortal and granted the gift of longevity.

34
00:02:44,340 --> 00:02:49,240
But who are you to touch my head?

35
00:03:12,340 --> 00:03:15,540
Go die!

36
00:03:43,300 --> 00:03:46,920
A skilled fighter hides his weapon and waits for the right chance.

37
00:03:46,920 --> 00:03:50,500
As still as a mountain and as agile as the thunder.

38
00:03:50,500 --> 00:03:54,460
As expected of the head of Shanqian Academy.

39
00:03:59,540 --> 00:04:03,560
I think that's enough, Zhuoqing.

40
00:04:09,100 --> 00:04:10,920
Master!

41
00:04:15,240 --> 00:04:16,900
Master.

42
00:04:19,960 --> 00:04:25,620
I suppose our duel should be the most vigorous one in nearly 30 years.

43
00:04:25,620 --> 00:04:27,940
Who on earth are you?

44
00:04:27,940 --> 00:04:29,620
Didn't I tell you?

45
00:04:29,620 --> 00:04:34,760
My name is Nangong Chunshui, an elegant scholar.

46
00:04:34,760 --> 00:04:37,160
Impossible. My phase...

47
00:04:37,160 --> 00:04:39,020
How boring.

48
00:04:39,020 --> 00:04:44,420
Why do you people keep talking about phases?

49
00:04:44,420 --> 00:04:47,260
Should we announce our phases before a fight?

50
00:04:47,260 --> 00:04:50,140
If yours is higher, I should surrender and let you win?

51
00:04:50,140 --> 00:04:52,680
That's not how it works, is it?

52
00:05:12,120 --> 00:05:14,900
Your disciple has great composure.

53
00:05:14,900 --> 00:05:17,340
He does justice to the Wind and Snow Sword.

54
00:05:22,100 --> 00:05:23,880
You...

55
00:05:29,980 --> 00:05:32,140
You are Li Changsheng?

56
00:05:32,140 --> 00:05:34,340
How many times do I have to repeat it?

57
00:05:34,340 --> 00:05:38,120
I'm Nangong Chunshui. You just won't remember.

58
00:05:38,780 --> 00:05:43,900
You entered the palace at the age of six with discontentment.

59
00:05:43,900 --> 00:05:47,220
Hence, you spent 30 years practicing to become the greatest martial artist.

60
00:05:47,220 --> 00:05:51,020
You could have dominated the world with your skills.

61
00:05:51,020 --> 00:05:52,900
However, you met me.

62
00:05:52,900 --> 00:05:55,100
Poor thing.

63
00:05:55,100 --> 00:05:59,020
I can kill you with the snap of my fingers.

64
00:05:59,020 --> 00:06:02,580
But no, I won't kill you.

65
00:06:02,580 --> 00:06:07,540
It's to give some face to that ruddy Emperor Tai'an.

66
00:06:07,540 --> 00:06:10,820
I left you a letter. Head back and read it carefully.

67
00:06:10,820 --> 00:06:15,920
You must... read it carefully.

68
00:06:18,300 --> 00:06:21,420
I will.

69
00:06:21,420 --> 00:06:23,460
Very well.

70
00:06:23,460 --> 00:06:27,620
I'm not going to kill you, but you are halfway in the Mental Phase of the Unknown,

71
00:06:27,620 --> 00:06:29,500
which is too high.

72
00:06:29,500 --> 00:06:32,800
Why don't you lower a phase?

73
00:06:43,620 --> 00:06:45,560
Master.

74
00:06:46,540 --> 00:06:51,500
Remember to remind your master to read that letter carefully.

75
00:06:51,500 --> 00:06:53,860
It's very important.

76
00:06:55,060 --> 00:06:57,200
Understood.

77
00:06:57,900 --> 00:07:00,620
Master, let's leave.

78
00:07:05,380 --> 00:07:07,500
Are you letting them go like that?

79
00:07:07,500 --> 00:07:11,000
These two might be a threat to be reckoned with.

80
00:07:11,660 --> 00:07:14,300
Aren't you a scholar?

81
00:07:14,300 --> 00:07:18,460
Scholars should be merciful. How can you simply kill?

82
00:07:18,460 --> 00:07:21,300
That's what monks do.

83
00:07:21,300 --> 00:07:26,180
We scholars can claim countless lives with our words in the court.

84
00:07:26,880 --> 00:07:28,660
Don't kill.

85
00:07:28,660 --> 00:07:33,600
If you want to kill, do it by yourself after I leave.

86
00:07:35,860 --> 00:07:39,380
Little Master, that's all I can do for you.

87
00:07:39,380 --> 00:07:41,580
I'm leaving.

88
00:08:18,380 --> 00:08:21,010
There were two of them

89
00:08:21,790 --> 00:08:24,600
but they made a formidable pair.

90
00:08:27,520 --> 00:08:32,620
How does that fool manage to hire such powerful helpers?

91
00:08:41,940 --> 00:08:46,400
Prince Qing, you are looking for me aren't you?

92
00:08:52,750 --> 00:08:59,750

93
00:09:20,940 --> 00:09:24,860
Young Master, you are a young talent with advanced martial skills.

94
00:09:24,860 --> 00:09:27,060
And I'm impressed by that.

95
00:09:27,060 --> 00:09:30,460
But that's enough for today.

96
00:09:32,180 --> 00:09:33,880
Jin Xian.

97
00:09:35,500 --> 00:09:37,220
You want to leave?

98
00:09:37,220 --> 00:09:38,760
Have you asked me about that?

99
00:09:38,760 --> 00:09:41,840
I might still have some strength left to fight desperately.

100
00:09:41,840 --> 00:09:43,560
You can't be sure of that.

101
00:09:43,560 --> 00:09:45,320
Even if you are strong,

102
00:09:45,320 --> 00:09:49,400
I'm afraid you might not stand a chance if we join hands.

103
00:09:49,400 --> 00:09:54,790
Rather than having both sides suffer, why don't we each take a step back?

104
00:09:58,914 --> 00:10:03,140
Next time we meet will it still be with drawn swords?

105
00:10:04,220 --> 00:10:06,420
I hope not.

106
00:10:25,860 --> 00:10:27,520
Who's there?

107
00:10:32,740 --> 00:10:34,460
Who are you?

108
00:10:34,460 --> 00:10:36,500
I'm Nangong Chunshui.

109
00:10:36,500 --> 00:10:40,540
I came here to see the successor to the Heart Sword and her daughter.

110
00:10:40,540 --> 00:10:42,820
Why do you want to see my daughter?

111
00:10:42,820 --> 00:10:46,680
To be frank, your daughter and I have a deal.

112
00:10:46,680 --> 00:10:48,600
She's now my disciple.

113
00:10:48,600 --> 00:10:51,200
Nonsense!

114
00:10:56,940 --> 00:11:00,460
I'm telling the truth. Why don't you believe me?

115
00:11:00,460 --> 00:11:03,100
- Mother. 
 - Hanyi, go back inside.

116
00:11:03,100 --> 00:11:05,260
Hanyi?

117
00:11:06,100 --> 00:11:08,220
Long time no see.

118
00:11:08,220 --> 00:11:10,460
Grandfather Li?

119
00:11:10,460 --> 00:11:13,460
Why do you look younger, Grandfather Li?

120
00:11:13,460 --> 00:11:15,540
What Grandfather Li?

121
00:11:15,540 --> 00:11:17,660
Call me Master.

122
00:11:18,940 --> 00:11:20,500
I...

123
00:11:36,940 --> 00:11:39,220
I have disappointed you, Master.

124
00:11:39,220 --> 00:11:41,020
I lost.

125
00:11:49,340 --> 00:11:50,840
I will accept my punishment.

126
00:11:50,840 --> 00:11:54,200
Please punish me, Master.

127
00:11:57,220 --> 00:11:59,600
I will accept my punishment too.

128
00:12:01,660 --> 00:12:03,680
There is no need for that.

129
00:12:05,780 --> 00:12:12,100
Leave Bali Dongjun alone from now on.

130
00:12:12,100 --> 00:12:15,880
I will explain it to His Majesty myself.

131
00:12:15,880 --> 00:12:17,760
Go back and cure your injuries.

132
00:12:17,760 --> 00:12:19,920
This time...

133
00:12:24,140 --> 00:12:26,800
I have miscalculated.

134
00:12:27,660 --> 00:12:30,940
So you need not blame yourselves.

