00:13:48,780 --> 00:13:51,340
You traveled for miles to help him.

149
00:13:51,340 --> 00:13:53,134
Don't you want to meet him?

150
00:13:54,540 --> 00:13:56,180
No.

151
00:13:56,180 --> 00:13:58,280
I'm a wanted criminal now.

152
00:13:58,280 --> 00:14:00,600
The matter of the Marquis Zhenxi's Mansion has just been settled.

153
00:14:00,600 --> 00:14:03,180
It's best not to drag him into more trouble.

154
00:14:03,740 --> 00:14:07,660
We will meet in due course.

155
00:14:14,500 --> 00:14:16,700
Yao'er. Master.

156
00:14:16,700 --> 00:14:19,000
And Second Senior's daughter?

157
00:14:20,780 --> 00:14:22,460
Why did you come back without telling us?

158
00:14:22,460 --> 00:14:27,320
If Mister Li hadn't returned, who would help you resolve the biggest challenge?

159
00:14:28,980 --> 00:14:31,900
You are dense. It's time to leave.

160
00:14:31,900 --> 00:14:36,049
- But my grandfather... 
 - Your grandfather has already returned to Qiandong City.

161
00:14:36,049 --> 00:14:40,300
After handling Grand Eunuch Zhuoqing, Mister Li went to the relay station.

162
00:14:40,300 --> 00:14:44,500
The Marquis left under the protection of the Pofang Army upon learning that you were safe.

163
00:14:44,500 --> 00:14:45,980
Don't worry.

164
00:14:45,980 --> 00:14:47,860
No worries.

165
00:14:49,420 --> 00:14:51,100
It's time to go back to Xueyue City.

166
00:14:51,100 --> 00:14:56,260
Don't forget that you are one of the city lords now.

167
00:14:56,260 --> 00:14:59,420
What about Changfeng? Isn't he a city lord as well?

168
00:14:59,420 --> 00:15:03,940
Well, he has something else to attend to.

169
00:15:03,940 --> 00:15:07,580
The matter in Tianqi City should be put to an end now.

170
00:15:07,580 --> 00:15:09,960
After returning to Xueyue City, stay away from court affairs

171
00:15:09,960 --> 00:15:13,960
and only be a simple martial artist. How about it?

172
00:15:16,660 --> 00:15:17,920
Certainly.

173
00:15:17,920 --> 00:15:20,240
Your family's marquisate is a hereditary title.

174
00:15:20,240 --> 00:15:22,580
You will become a marquis.

175
00:15:22,580 --> 00:15:27,040
It holds great power above the people.

176
00:15:27,040 --> 00:15:29,280
Are you sure you want to quit?

177
00:15:29,280 --> 00:15:32,560
I never wish for wars. I came here for the sake of Grandfather.

178
00:15:32,560 --> 00:15:37,320
Since this is over, well, let's go back to the Martial World.

179
00:15:38,300 --> 00:15:39,860
Very well.

180
00:15:39,860 --> 00:15:43,900
Admiring the blossoms over a drink with friends is a wonderful time, one that can never be returned to after years.

181
00:15:43,900 --> 00:15:47,420
Let's go back to the Martial World.

182
00:15:50,860 --> 00:15:52,480
Let's go.

183
00:16:22,057 --> 00:16:24,220

184
00:16:24,220 --> 00:16:26,160
State Preceptor.

185
00:16:27,220 --> 00:16:32,580
Is my plan somewhat naive?

186
00:16:34,100 --> 00:16:37,780
I wouldn't say your plan is naive.

187
00:16:37,780 --> 00:16:40,540
It's all for the sake of Beili.

188
00:16:40,540 --> 00:16:46,720
However, what you have seen is only a few decades.

189
00:16:46,720 --> 00:16:52,220
What Li Changsheng has seen is a few hundred years, right?

190
00:16:53,900 --> 00:17:01,420
Mister Li is probably the guardian of Beili.

191
00:17:01,420 --> 00:17:06,460
Whether he has groomed the peerless Prince Langya

192
00:17:06,460 --> 00:17:09,780
or taken Baili Dongjun as his disciple,

193
00:17:09,780 --> 00:17:13,260
it's all part of his strategy to protect the nation.

194
00:17:13,860 --> 00:17:17,100
Do some people really live for hundreds of years?

195
00:17:18,866 --> 00:17:24,320
In sects with secret martial skills, some indeed become deities.

196
00:17:24,920 --> 00:17:28,540
However, living for a hundred years isn't easy.

197
00:17:28,540 --> 00:17:35,100
Living for hundreds of years would demand a price beyond what ordinary people can endure.

198
00:17:35,860 --> 00:17:42,440
Naturally, they have to bear the responsibilities that ordinary people cannot bear.

199
00:17:48,360 --> 00:17:50,840
Now I understand.

200
00:17:58,660 --> 00:18:02,420

201
00:18:14,426 --> 00:18:18,653

202
00:18:29,060 --> 00:18:31,240
I, Sikong Changfeng, the disciple of Xueyue City,

203
00:18:31,240 --> 00:18:34,240
would like to challenge Liu Xiaochen, the King of Spear, to a duel.

204
00:18:43,420 --> 00:18:45,420
I, Sikong Changfeng, the disciple of Xueyue City,

205
00:18:45,420 --> 00:18:48,600
would like to challenge Liu Xiaochen, the King of Spear, to a duel.

206
00:19:00,931 --> 00:19:04,780

207
00:19:04,780 --> 00:19:07,320
Are you Liu Xiaochen, the King of Spear?

208
00:19:07,320 --> 00:19:10,540
You want to challenge me to a spear duel?

209
00:19:12,260 --> 00:19:14,160
Please show me your skills.

210
00:19:20,013 --> 00:19:23,713

211
00:19:26,180 --> 00:19:31,140
Master, you haven't told me why you brought Second Senior's daughter along?

212
00:19:31,140 --> 00:19:33,660
Let me reintroduce her to you.

213
00:19:33,660 --> 00:19:37,100
This is your first junior sister.

214
00:19:37,740 --> 00:19:41,900
Throughout my life, I have only taken three disciples.

215
00:19:43,500 --> 00:19:46,880
No wonder Changfeng is the third city lord of Xueyue City.

216
00:19:46,880 --> 00:19:49,580
Turns out the second city lord is here.

217
00:19:49,580 --> 00:19:51,480
Senior.

218
00:19:52,620 --> 00:19:54,540
Good girl.

219
00:19:54,540 --> 00:19:58,160
This is my spouse.

220
00:19:58,160 --> 00:20:01,120
Ignore him. My name is Yue Yao.

221
00:20:01,900 --> 00:20:04,300
Sister Yue Yao.

222
00:20:08,220 --> 00:20:10,860
This darned Xiao Ruofeng.

223
00:20:10,860 --> 00:20:13,020
Is he really my junior?

224
00:20:13,020 --> 00:20:16,660
Wait. Now, there's also another Dongba.

225
00:20:16,660 --> 00:20:19,020
He's also my junior, right?

226
00:20:19,020 --> 00:20:21,960
Who am I? I'm their senior.

227
00:20:21,960 --> 00:20:25,260
They summoned me to chase after a runaway bride.

228
00:20:25,260 --> 00:20:27,820
Oh, come on. Even the government office wouldn't give a fig about that.

229
00:20:27,820 --> 00:20:31,700
And also that Ye Dingzhi. He's the son of General Ye Yu, whom I admire the most.

230
00:20:31,700 --> 00:20:33,540
I doubt I can catch him.

231
00:20:33,540 --> 00:20:36,660
They throw all the difficult tasks at me. I'm done with it.

232
00:20:36,660 --> 00:20:39,300
At worst, I will quit being a general.

233
00:20:39,300 --> 00:20:42,820
Maybe I should go home and apologize to my wife.

234
00:20:42,820 --> 00:20:48,460
Why do I suddenly find that having this fellow as my second senior is an embarrassment?

235
00:20:48,980 --> 00:20:50,640
Lei'er.

236
00:20:51,300 --> 00:20:53,100
Second Senior.

237
00:20:53,100 --> 00:20:56,480
Xiao Dongba? What are you doing here?

238
00:20:56,480 --> 00:21:00,660
Hanyi, why are you here, too? It's so far from home.

239
00:21:00,660 --> 00:21:02,500
Who are you?

240
00:21:02,500 --> 00:21:04,640
I'm your master.

241
00:21:06,480 --> 00:21:09,740
Just anyone can talk down to me when I'm down on my luck, huh?

242
00:21:09,740 --> 00:21:14,980
I left Tianqi City for a few days and you, little bloke, are acting tough against me.

243
00:21:14,980 --> 00:21:17,420
I am the Second Senior in Jixia Academy,

244
00:21:17,420 --> 00:21:22,660
Mister Li's direct disciple, Young Master Zhuomo, Lei Mengsha.

245
00:21:37,660 --> 00:21:40,060
Mister Li's direct disciple, huh?

246
00:21:40,060 --> 00:21:42,260
Jeez, you and your whining.

247
00:21:42,260 --> 00:21:45,180
Prince Langya is nothing. Beat him up if you are not convinced.

248
00:21:45,180 --> 00:21:47,040
Why are you complaining here?

249
00:21:54,180 --> 00:21:55,740
Wait.

250
00:21:57,300 --> 00:22:00,460
You are Master, right?

251
00:22:00,460 --> 00:22:04,420
Gosh. Why are you wearing a mask to freak me out?

252
00:22:09,660 --> 00:22:12,020
Master, my daughter is over there.

253
00:22:12,020 --> 00:22:13,840
Please do me a favor.

254
00:22:15,340 --> 00:22:16,880
Get lost.

