00:33:17,800 --> 00:33:22,100
 In the 18th year of Taihe's era, Emperor Tai'an of Beili fell gravely ill.

396
00:33:22,100 --> 00:33:24,600
 The struggle vying for the throne escalated.

397
00:33:24,600 --> 00:33:29,800
