443
00:38:43,500 --> 00:38:48,100
 I remember one winter when there was a heavy snowfall.

444
00:38:48,100 --> 00:38:55,260
 Even when I think of it now, I still feel the biting cold.

445
00:38:56,440 --> 00:39:03,720
